{"word":"G329 - ἀναζωπυρέω - anazōpyréō - an-ad-zo-poor-eh'-o - Stir up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναζωπυρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anazōpyréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ad-zo-poor-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Stir up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அனல்மூட்டு, எழுப்பிவிடு"},{"paragraph":"to be enkindled, to gain strength"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G2226 - ζῶον - zōon - dzo'-on/2226\">G2226</a> and <a href=\"#/G4442 - πῦρ - pŷr - poor/4442\">G4442</a>; to <i>re-enkindle:</i> - stir up.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}